{"tid":487359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共要在外企發展黨組織？ 德國商會：無必要！警告撤資！","createTime":"2017-12-02T16:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T02:51:54.000Z","uid":43189,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"965eed2aab2f5737bf3b05d7ba7c2586f67b513a","tid":487359,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"【非第三方政黨負責外企經營】<br />\n【無義務無必要在內部擴張黨組織】<br />\n<br />\n德國駐華工商總會日前在官方網頁發布聲明，高度關注在華德國企業被施壓要求發展壯大中共黨組織一事。聲明強調外企的經營由外企負責人而非第三方政黨負責，企業無義務也無必要在內部擴張第三方政黨組織。<br />\n<br />\n商會警告如果這一趨勢繼續蔓延，將考慮全面退出和終止在華業務和對華投資計劃。<br />\n<br />\n#黨領導一切<br />\n#黨委書記大定董事長大<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1571539696323844&amp;id=265944843550009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1571539696323844%26id%3D265944843550009&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI62zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=a8a84184\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1571539696323844&amp;id=265944843550009</a>"},{"pid":"1faa1e100c3ece4cc8057e3e58bbcdee0b1d413c","tid":487359,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58184641ad937a5ccbef6f0231230a7dbdb2e2a8","tid":487359,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"而家大陸好多德國合資車廠喎"},{"pid":"8eba43d3cd75612bf84148197062e76177eac326","tid":487359,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家大陸好多德國合資車廠喎</blockquote><br />\n收歸國有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44ad596c3908832f20019314a44d2a4a8dc58bd","tid":487359,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家大陸好多德國合資車廠喎</blockquote><br />\n做生意唔一定要擦鞋"},{"pid":"057dd93dd53d8b38ac